derivation: from G303 (ἀνατέλλω) and the base of G5056 (ἀνατέλλω);
kjv_def: (a-, make to) rise, at the rising of, spring (up), be up
outline:
1. rise
    1. to cause to rise
      1. of the earth bring forth plants
    2. to rise, arise, to rise from, be descended from
      1. of sun moon and stars)
